OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FOutbreaks of patchy rain will
OL,6,Fsink south across Wales on Monday,
OL,7,Fclearing to sunny spells during the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Feeling rather chilly for
OL,9,Fthe time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FRemaining changeable on Tuesday with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of patchy rain clearing
OL,14,Fsouth. Turning blustery with sunny
OL,15,Fspells and heavy showers both
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday. Feeling
OL,17,Fchilly, with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
